        SCIENCE B9 THE STRAITS TIMES SATURDAY, OCTOBER 24, 2020 | | | Health Check Podcast What is the best anti-ageing diet? In ageing research, scientists strive to find ways to improve healthspan - the period of life that is spent in good health. They are studying different methods, including calorie restrictio­n and fasting. So, what is the best anti-ageing diet and are there foods to eat or avoid, or supplement­s to take when it comes to delaying ageing? ST senior health correspond­ent Joyce Teo speaks with Professor Brian Kennedy, the director of the NUHS Centre for Healthy Longevity to find out more.
